title: Day 466
content:
# Day 466

The ability to convey your messages in as few words as possible reflects a deep understanding of what you are talking about. This data says a lot.

![[https://twitter.com/TheBlackHorse65/status/1674800284235603968?s=20](https://twitter.com/TheBlackHorse65/status/1674800284235603968?s=20)](https://miro.medium.com/1*YKi3WSvPI9AEfR48yTgumQ.png)

Also Twitter has kind of been a shit show today and introduced limits to how many times you could view tweets. Odell has been pretty spot on about Twitter Blue being a trojan horse for digital ID. Maybe true maybe not true but I lean towards the former.

![](https://miro.medium.com/1*T7HDqPLqY0EX8D8rhvKZ0g.png)

Wonder if this has anything to do with it? Potentially.

![](https://miro.medium.com/0*C5TYtH7mK6zavyPD)

![](https://miro.medium.com/0*6-LO1DZZyk_t-XdO)

Interesting summer. I need to stop spending so much time online and smell the roses. It has been so special being back in Jax seeing my family. Cyber space is mid. Real life is where the real value can be found :)

7/1/23

Conor Jay Chepenik
